OL,7,FAttack coach Rob Howley has left
OL,8,FWales' coaching staff, following
OL,9,FWarren Gatland out of the door in a
OL,10,Ftumultuous week for the Welsh Rugby
OL,11,FUnion.
OL,13,FGatland approached CEO Abi Tierney in
OL,14,Fthe wake of the defeat in Italy - a
OL,15,Frecord 14th in a row - to say he no
OL,16,Flonger felt like the right man to take
OL,17,FWales forward.
