OL,7,FCardiff Rugby head coach Matt Sherratt
OL,8,Fhas stepped in to lead Wales on an
OL,9,Finterim basis until the end of the Six
OL,10,FNations.
OL,12,FHowley's departure from his coaching
OL,13,Frole with the senior men's national
OL,14,Fside, comes as little surprise.
OL,16,FSherratt has always been an attack
OL,17,Fcoach before getting the top job at
OL,18,FCardiff, so will have his own
OL,19,Fattacking philosophies.
