OL,4,Cboss Matt Sherratt calls up three
OL,5,Cplayers
OL,7,FHowever, he is still contracted to the
OL,8,FWRU and it remains to be seen whether
OL,9,Fhe will continue the work that he has
OL,10,Fbeen doing with the age-grade pathway
OL,11,Fsystem. Elsewhere, Sherratt has
OL,12,Frecalled three players to his squad as
OL,13,Fhe deals with injuries from the
OL,14,Fopening two games.
OL,16,FFly-halves Gareth Anscombe and Jarrod
OL,17,FEvans return to the fold. Anscombe's
OL,18,Fomission from the off was a surprise
OL,19,Fand Evans has not played Test rugby
OL,20,Ffor Wales since 2021.
