OL,7,FIn-form Gloucester centre Max
OL,8,FLlewellyn is also recalled. Gatland's
OL,9,Fcall to leave him out of the squad was
OL,10,Fa surprise after he started all three
OL,11,Fgames in the autumn and was the top
OL,12,Ftry-scorer in the England Premiership
OL,13,Fwhen the squad was announced.
OL,15,FThere is bad news, though. Owen Watkin
OL,16,Fand Liam Williams have both been ruled
OL,17,Fout of the rest of the Championship
OL,18,Fafter sustaining knee injuries against
OL,19,FFrance on the opening night.
