OL,8,FCardiff against Connacht this weekend
OL,9,Fbefore arriving in camp on Monday.
OL,11,FHe will have four training sessions to
OL,12,Fprepare Wales to face Ireland, who
OL,13,Farrive in Cardiff next week hunting a
OL,14,FGrand Slam.
